Given this political fundraising email, respond with the name of the committee in the disclaimer that begins with Paid for by but does not include Paid for by, the committee address or the treasurer name. If no committee is present, return "None". Do not include any other text, no yapping.
name: Mike Johnson
email: info@freedomtrainalert.com
subject: This is the final push
body: One last try… Peter, I’ve emailed. I’ve texted. I’ve done everything I canto garner the grassroots support our campaigns need to take back Congress –but with neck-and-neck polling and record fundraising numbers released fromthe Democrats, we need to DOUBLE DOWN on our efforts! My team has reached outto the top patriots on our list, and you’re one of them.Can I count on you togive a $5, $10, or $25 gift to keep our campaigns running? I’M PLEADING!GIVE $5 GIFT GIVE $10 GIFT GIVE $25 GIFT We’re running out of time to turnthings around. If I can count on you, please act now.I’ll check back and hopeto see your name on the list of patriots who’ve answered this call to action.Best, Speaker Mike Johnson Unsubscribe Paid for by Mike Johnson for Louisiana
